articles.title: Google releases its own ‘reasoning’ AI model - TechCrunch
articles.description: Google has released what it's calling a new "reasoning" AI model to rival OpenAI's o1 — but it's in the experimental stages.
articles.content:
Google has released what it’s calling a new “reasoning” AI model but it’s in the experimental stages, and from our brief testing, there’s certainly room for improvement.
